==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: American plan
<hw>A*mer"i*can plan</hw>. <def>In hotels, a plan upon which guests pay
for both room and board by the day, week, or other convenient period; --
contrasted with <contr>European plan</contr>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>American Protective Association</ent>⟦br⟧
